ike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T01:47:27.000Z","msg":"楚日天無論做乜最後都會柒的詛咒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇到去佢第一次嘗試去復活隊友果度就冇睇<br />\n因為果時zxttty又斷更<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後尾知道佢完咗本都冇勇氣補返<br />\n因為收到風結局係日天最後都係打破唔到柒的詛咒最後死埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得曙光個主角設定同隔離卷土嘅最終進化一樣咁趕客<br />\n方森岩又係一出場好似好高智商咁<br />\n之後智戰佈局又係瘋狂計錯計漏數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結果每卷一百章，頭八十章就係睇一個弱智仔嘗試玩智戰結果比人瘋狂sm，尾二十章就睇佢夾硬靠肌肉沖沖沖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"192e2c3538c08d88d829cab2c9f2e2ca38c07a52","tid":878062,"uid":100809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36f6268e2dae74c084a8605649968a886cd64fe5","tid":878062,"uid":18319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ffe0ad25dddbde730c2219d3acad1f15eb19d59","tid":878062,"uid":136640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T01:17:58.000Z","msg":"睇左陣無限曙光 覺得男主中二病爆發 睇唔落去"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T01:22:52.000Z","msg":"楚浩無論做咩都有浸柒味同想打冷震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T03:32:47.000Z","msg":"楚浩個人物係楚軒+fate zero個衛宮切x混合體<br />\n但係又寫唔到衛官果種為正義放棄好多野既痛苦 <br />\n搞到好似個小學雞係咁嗌我要正義咁 中二到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45cca7f6c4ff13570e83d7c7e7e8cf24fb07e5b3","tid":878062,"uid":49981,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b159d14072b7618894e06b4941ca8eac519f612e","tid":878062,"uid":75815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T22:39:30.000Z","msg":"自問聰明，但冇套野d人咁神<br />\n樓主有咩資源可以幫助到所謂既聰明人發揮到？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T05:35:50.000Z","msg":"要了解一